{"tid":290541,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[星座撚] 想追女求評","createTime":"2017-06-20T00:12:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-20T03:49:54.000Z","uid":1083,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4a3855ade652aa19c57dde2e7d283e1302d7be22","tid":290541,"uid":1083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T00:12:53.000Z","msg":"屌你啦究竟智商有幾低先會信星座<br />\n不嬲習慣見到星座post就入去block撚晒班智障，點知block到手軟都未block晒<br />\n咩邊個星座出名毒，邊個出名咸濕，個撚個連登毒撚都咸濕架啦，儲齊12個星座俾你都得呀<br />\n咩獅子男處女女成日鬧交點好，話你唔夾係咪即刻分手呀，唔通我同我老母星座唔夾就離家出走咩，拎個問題出嚟講好過啦<br />\n仲信星座嘅一係順手信埋生肖，買多本通勝睇吓邊日宜溝女，一係去照吓個腦啦"},{"pid":"31e3afaeae914edc4ad2deefb692e5e9f32c8ec8","tid":290541,"uid":53619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T00:15:20.000Z","msg":"咩姐<br />\n好多女都信星座唔講星座少個話題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1db186f93aec794cd50c29cca462b0421fcbb19b","tid":290541,"uid":1083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T00:21:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩姐<br />\n好多女都信星座唔講星座少個話題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n試吓溝啲智力正常嘅女"},{"pid":"8f69bb042630ae884479ca1d932672564a8a7bce","tid":290541,"uid":1083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T00:46:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adae20b935ce3a32c659069f8e396c316e233069","tid":290541,"uid":1083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T01:24:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b7039ad2eb8baac8df5cfb7604b2c2d1131c494","tid":290541,"uid":1083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T03:49:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}